Class ContactDataVersionManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • mobisocial.musubi.model.helpers.ManagerBase
      • mobisocial.musubi.model.helpers.ContactDataVersionManager

  • public class ContactDataVersionManager
extends ManagerBase
    manages the state that tracks which email addresses, etc. have been modified in the address book. also deals with the sync state table which tracks things like the max contact id seen, etc
